        {
            "_id": "K5dIa5gCC7aePzQf",
            "data": {
                "actionCategory": {
                    "value": "offensive"
                },
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When the accursed forge-spurned critically hits a target with its <em>soul chain</em>, the chain leeches away a portion of the target's soul. The target must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:36] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is drained 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 2} from the pain.</p>"
                },
                "requirements": {
                    "value": ""
                },
